'''提格兰·列沃诺维奇·彼得罗相'''（{{lang-ru|Тигра́н Лево́нович Петрося́н}}，{{lang-hy|Տիգրան Պետրոսյան}}，{{bd|1984年|9月17日}}），[[亚美尼亚|亚美尼亚]][[国际象棋|国际象棋]]棋手、[[国际象棋特级大师|特级大师]]。

彼得罗相出生时，他的父亲决定以首位亚美尼亚裔[[国际象棋世界冠军|世界冠军]][[提格兰·彼得罗相|提格兰·彼得罗相]]的名字为他命名。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/from_our_own_correspondent/8275099.stm | title=Armenia revels in its chess prowess | work=BBC News | date=2009-09-26 | accessdate=2010-05-25 | archive-date=2017-01-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116165519/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/from_our_own_correspondent/8275099.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>

彼得罗相于2004年获得[[国际象棋特级大师|国际象棋特级大师]]称号。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chesscafe.com/text/misha19.pdf|title=Interview with Tigran L. Petrosian|last=Savinov|first=Misha|publisher=[[chesscafe.com|chesscafe.com]]|accessdate=2009-08-26|archive-date=2005-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050222204100/http://www.chesscafe.com/text/misha19.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>2008年，他作为亚美尼亚队的成员获得了[[2008年国际象棋奥林匹克|第38届国际象棋奥林匹克]]团体冠军。.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://chess-results.com/tnr16314.aspx?art=20&lan=1&flag=30&m=-1&wi=1000&snr=9|title=Olympiad Dresden 2008 Open|date=2009-02-05|publisher=Chess-Results.com|accessdate=22 March 2011|archive-date=2011-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111002043206/http://chess-results.com/tnr16314.aspx?art=20&lan=1&flag=30&m=-1&wi=1000&snr=9|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年，他还成为了亚美尼亚[[菲舍尔任意制象棋|菲舍尔任意制象棋]]首位冠军。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.armchess.am/news11-02.htm|title=Tigran L. Petrosian – Chess960 Champion|date=2011-02-01|publisher=Armchess.am|accessdate=29 January 2012|archive-date=2011-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110531155324/http://www.armchess.am/news11-02.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>之后，他于2012年、2013年连续两年成为亚美尼亚国际象棋全国冠军。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://chess-results.com/tnr66350.aspx?art=1&lan=1|title=2012 Armenian Rapid Championship|date=2012-02-18|publisher=Chess-Results.com|accessdate=19 February 2012|archive-date=2014-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103041148/http://chess-results.com/tnr66350.aspx?art=1&lan=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fide.com/component/content/article/4-tournaments/6767-armenian-chess-championships-2013.html|title=Armenian Chess Championships 2013|date=2013-01-25|publisher=FIDE|accessdate=18 January 2014|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112072914/https://www.fide.com/component/content/article/4-tournaments/6767-armenian-chess-championships-2013.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

